# Siftly-Kimi-K2.5 — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# Optimized for Moonshot AI (Kimi K2.5) — OpenAI-compatible API
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Database — SQLite file path (no changes needed for local dev)
DATABASE_URL="file:./prisma/dev.db"
# ── Moonshot AI / Kimi K2.5 Configuration ────────────────────────────
# REQUIRED: Your Moonshot API Key
# Get yours at: https://platform.moonshot.cn (starts with sk-)
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-moonshot-api-key-here
# REQUIRED: Moonshot API Base URL (OpenAI-compatible)
OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.moonshot.cn/v1
# Optional: Specific Kimi model (defaults to kimi-k2.5)
# Available models: kimi-k2.5, kimi-k2.5-turbo, kimi-k2.5-preview
OPENAI_MODEL=kimi-k2.5
# ── Legacy Anthropic (Disabled) ─────────────────────────────────────
# These are disabled in this fork. Use OpenAI/Moonshot settings above.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=
# ── Access control (optional) ────────────────────────────────────────
# Set BOTH to enable HTTP Basic Auth on the entire app.
# Leave unset for unrestricted local access (the default).
# Recommended when exposing Siftly via a public URL (e.g. Cloudflare Tunnel).
# SIFTLY_USERNAME=admin
# SIFTLY_PASSWORD=your-passphrase-here
Commit message: feat: update .env.example for Moonshot/Kimi K2.5
